text: Aleksander Rozmus (18 January 1901 - 18 April 1986) was a Polish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1986 deaths Category:Polish male ski jumpers Category:Polish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Poland Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Poland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1928 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1928 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zakopane
